U.K. Stocks Decline; Lloyds Banking, Schroders Lead FTSE 100 Index Lower

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-05-05T09:58:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/u-k-stocks-decline-lloyds-banking-schroders-lead-ftse-100-index-lower.html
U.K. stocks declined, led by Lloyds
Banking Group Plc and Schroders Plc. The benchmark FTSE 100
Index lost 27.41, or 0.5 percent, to 5,956.66 as of 10:57 a.m.
in  London .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
